Maple stxBrain Analyis - Anterior and Posterior Samples

Carter Allen

11/20/2021

Packages

library(Seurat)
library(SeuratData)
library(maple)
library(patchwork)
library(ggplot2)

Install and Load Data

# Load data
InstallData("stxBrain")
brain1 <- LoadData("stxBrain", type = "anterior1")
brain2 <- LoadData("stxBrain", type = "anterior2")
brain3 <- LoadData("stxBrain", type = "posterior1")
brain4 <- LoadData("stxBrain", type = "posterior2")

Process and Merge Samples

brain1 <- SCTransform(brain1, assay = "Spatial", verbose = FALSE)
brain2 <- SCTransform(brain2, assay = "Spatial", verbose = FALSE)
brain3 <- SCTransform(brain3, assay = "Spatial", verbose = FALSE)
brain4 <- SCTransform(brain4, assay = "Spatial", verbose = FALSE)

brain <- merge(brain1,brain2)
brain <- merge(brain,brain3)
brain <- merge(brain,brain4)
DefaultAssay(brain) <- "SCT"
VariableFeatures(brain) <- c(VariableFeatures(brain1),
                             VariableFeatures(brain2),
                             VariableFeatures(brain3),
                             VariableFeatures(brain4))
brain <- RunPCA(brain)

Model Fitting

PC Features

brain_fit_PCs_K10 <- fit_maple(brain,K = 10,emb = "PCs",covars = "region")

Visualization

# plot labels
brain$maple_labels_PCs_K10 <- factor(brain_fit_PCs_K10$z,
                                     levels = sort(as.numeric(unique(brain_fit_PCs_K10$z))))
Idents(brain) <- "maple_labels_PCs_K10"
z_plots_K10_list <- SpatialDimPlot(brain,
                                   label = TRUE,
                                   combine = FALSE,
                                   label.size = 4,
                                   repel = TRUE)
z_plots_K10 <- z_plots_K10_list[[1]] + z_plots_K10_list[[3]] + 
  z_plots_K10_list[[2]] + z_plots_K10_list[[4]] + 
  plot_layout(nrow = 2, byrow = TRUE)
z_plots_K10

# plot coefficients
delta_plots_K10 <- spruce::plot_deltas(brain_fit_PCs_K10)
delta_plots_K10

# get scores
post_scores <- spruce::get_scores(brain_fit_PCs_K10)
brain@meta.data <- cbind(brain@meta.data,post_scores)

# plot scores
u_plots_K10_list <- SpatialFeaturePlot(brain,features = "u_score",combine = FALSE)
u_plots_K10 <- u_plots_K10_list[[1]] + u_plots_K10_list[[3]] + 
  u_plots_K10_list[[2]] + u_plots_K10_list[[4]] + 
  plot_layout(nrow = 2, byrow = TRUE)
u_plots_K10

k1_plots_K10_list <- SpatialFeaturePlot(brain,features = "k1_score", combine = FALSE)
k1_plots_K10 <- k1_plots_K10_list[[1]] + k1_plots_K10_list[[3]] + 
  k1_plots_K10_list[[2]] + k1_plots_K10_list[[4]] + 
  plot_layout(nrow = 2, byrow = TRUE)
k1_plots_K10

# plot proportions
colnames(brain_fit_PCs_K10$W) <- c("Intercept","Posterior")
brain_fit_PCs_K10$z <- factor(brain_fit_PCs_K10$z,
                              levels = sort(as.numeric(unique(brain_fit_PCs_K10$z))))
brain_fit_PCs_K10$W[,"Posterior"] <- ifelse(brain_fit_PCs_K10$W[,"Posterior"] == 1, "Posterior","Anterior")

grouped_bar_plot_K10 <- plot_props_grouped(brain_fit_PCs_K10, group = "Posterior")+ 
  theme(text = element_text(size = 20))
grouped_bar_plot_K10

stacked_bar_plot_K10 <- plot_props_stacked(brain_fit_PCs_K10, group = "Posterior")+ 
  theme(text = element_text(size = 20))
stacked_bar_plot_K10

pie_plot_K10 <- plot_props_pie(brain_fit_PCs_K10, group = "Posterior") + 
  theme(text = element_text(size = 20))
pie_plot_K10

# plot alluvial
plot_props_alluvial(brain_fit_PCs_K10, group = "Posterior")
